(83, 1, '2024-02-11 00:15:35', '2024-02-11 00:15:35', '<h1></h1>\r\nHello there! I\'m Don Sijo, a passionate web developer originally from Kerala, India, currently residing in the beautiful land of Canada. It\'s been an exciting journey since I arrived here five months ago, and I\'ve been captivated by the charm and opportunities this country has to offer.\r\n\r\nCurrently, I\'m a student at Georgian College, pursuing a course in Interactive Media Design with a focus on web development. Throughout my time at college, I\'ve delved into various programming languages and web technologies, honing my skills in building captivating and user-friendly websites.\r\n\r\nOne of my proudest achievements is the creation of my personal portfolio website from scratch. With a blend of HTML, CSS, and JavaScript, I crafted a showcase of my skills and experiences, demonstrating my proficiency in web development and design. This project reflects my dedication to continuous learning and my commitment to delivering high-quality work.\r\n\r\nLooking ahead, my goal is to immerse myself in an innovative space as a web developer, where I can contribute my expertise and collaborate with like-minded individuals to create impactful digital experiences.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-157\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/screenshot-1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"571\" height=\"571\" />', 'Home', '', 'trash', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'home__trashed', '', '', '2024-03-17 02:52:10', '2024-03-17 02:52:10', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?page_id=83', 0, 'page', '', 0),
